                                <p class=" text-justify " style="font-size:13px">1.1 Sagi Rama Krishanam Raju Alumni Association of North America, Inc is a 501(c)(3) organization registered in Florida with EIN number 92-2398357 and has its registered office at 10253 Estuary Dr., Tampa, FL 33647, USA (“SAANA”). SAANA operates an online donation service website (“Website”) providing various services (“Services”), including the collection and processing of donations received (the “Donations”) from individual donors (the “Donors”). SAANA, Inc also administers grant programs independently from the Website.

